 strong late finish at Wanganui over 1600m when finishing runner-up as the favourite by a head. He is likely to settle back again from another wide gate, but if the gaps come at the right time, he can have the last say. 2. DESERT MYSTIC brings winning form after a sharp closing effort to score over 1600m at Hawera on a good track 17 days ago. He stays in the same class, and he can repeat the dose, especially if the track is not too wet. 6. DOLLYBIRD fought on gamely at Trentham over 1400m and only just missed, finishing second by half-a-length, and she is as tough as they come. Each way claims again. 11. UP THE ANTI has just battled in this class since winning at BM65 level at Ellerslie on New Year's Day. He was not too far away at Pukekohe last start, and he can spice up some top 4 combos in this. 12. JUNGLE JANE failed to fire as the favourite at Trentham 3 weeks ago over 1400m An extra 200m will suit her, so follow your money.\",\"runners\":[4,2,6,11,12],\"exclusive\":true}","tips":{"tipType":"Standard","tipster":"NZ TAB","tipRunnerNumbers":[1,2,8,11]},"ratings":[{"ratingType":"Rating","ratingRunnerNumbers":[1,12,7,6]},{"ratingType":"Last12Months","ratingRunnerNumbers":[4,2,11,12]},{"ratingType":"Recent","ratingRunnerNumbers":[8,10,6,4]},{"ratingType":"Distance","ratingRunnerNumbers":[1,8,7,11]},{"ratingType":"Class","ratingRunnerNumbers":[4,10,7,12]},{"ratingType":"Time","ratingRunnerNumbers":[12,1,4,6]},{"ratingType":"Overall","ratingRunnerNumbers":[1,4,12,8]}],"multiLegApproximates":[],"betTypes":[{"wageringProduct":"Win","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":8,"venueMnemonic":"OTK","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Place","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":8,"venueMnemonic":"OTK","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Quinella","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":8,"venueMnemonic":"OTK","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Exacta","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":8,"venueMnemonic":"OTK","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Duet","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":8,"venueMnemonic":"OTK","raceType":"R"}},{"wag